text: Mryaushlinsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Nizhnebikkuzinsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 109 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Mrakovo, 12 km from Nizhnebikkuzino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Mryaushlinsky
